Package us.ullberg.startpunkt.rest

Class ThemeColors

java.lang.Object
us.ullberg.startpunkt.rest.ThemeColors
public class ThemeColors extends Object
Represents the color scheme for a theme. Contains colors for background, text, emphasis, and accents.
